'''全儲備銀行業務'''也被稱為'''百分之百儲備銀行業務'''，相對於[[部分儲備銀行業務|部分儲備銀行業務]]，這類銀行需要具備相對應[[存款|儲戶]]所存入的[[現金|現金]]的所有額度，讓存款者在提款時滿足他們的需求。舉例來說，顧客們的[[活期存款|活期存款]]帳戶或是[[往來戶口|支票戶口]]這類的存款都不能被銀行作為[[借贷|借貸]]的流動資金，因為這些資金是銀行顧客們需要資金時要立即滿足他們需求的金額。相對應的，[[定期存款|定期存款]]則沒有這方面的要求與限制，在定期存款期間，銀行可以不用立即履行顧客們的金錢需求<ref>A Program for Monetary Reform</ref>。

在過去的貨幣改革，充分儲備銀行業務被許多經濟學家廣泛提出，特別是在1935年有一群經濟學家，其中包括[[欧文·费雪|欧文·费雪]]，這些思維主要是對於[[大蕭條|大蕭條]]做出回應<ref>{{Citation|last=Fisher|first=Irving|title=100% Money|year=1935}}</ref><ref name="Weisenthal">{{Cite web|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/banning-banks-2014-4|title=BAN ALL THE BANKS: Here's The Wild Idea That People Are Starting To Take Seriously|publisher=Business Insider|last1=Weisenthal|first1=Joe|accessdate=2016-07-02|archive-date=2020-11-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201101111904/https://www.businessinsider.com/banning-banks-2014-4|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而在現今的世界中，沒有任何金融體系特別提到全儲備銀行業務，主要是由於銀行業藉由合約來滿足存款準備金比率。

== 全儲備銀行業務的觀點 ==
經濟學家[[米爾頓·佛利民|米爾頓·佛利民]]認為支票帳戶需要具有百分之百的儲備要求<ref>{{Citation|last=Solow|first=Robert M.|title=Financial crises, contagion, and the lender of last resort|date=March 28, 2002|page=203|chapter=On the Lender of Last Resort|chapterurl=https://books.google.com/books?id=2486Jp8TjEcC&pg=PA201&dq=financial+crises,+contagion,+and+the+lender+of+last+resort&source=gbs_toc_r&cad=9#v=onepage&q&f=false|publisher=Oxford University Press|isbn=978-0-19-924721-9|accessdate=2016-07-02|archive-date=2019-07-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190726145024/https://books.google.com/books?id=2486Jp8TjEcC&pg=PA201&dq=financial+crises,+contagion,+and+the+lender+of+last+resort&source=gbs_toc_r&cad=9#v=onepage&q&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref> ，另外[[勞倫斯·克里寇夫|勞倫斯·克里寇夫]]也呼籲應該終結部分準備金銀行業務<ref>{{Citation|last=Kotlikoff|first=Laurence J.|title=A Banking System We Can Trust|date=April 23, 2009|url=http://people.bu.edu/kotlikoff/newweb/Abankingsystemwecantrust_4_2009.pdf|last2=Leamer|first2=Edward|journal=Forbes.com|accessdate=September 14, 2010|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110604020252/http://people.bu.edu/kotlikoff/newweb/Abankingsystemwecantrust_4_2009.pdf|archivedate=2011年6月4日}}</ref>。[[奧地利經濟學派|奧地利經濟學派]]的經濟學家[[穆瑞·羅斯巴德|穆瑞·羅斯巴德]]也曾撰文指出不能符合全儲備銀行業務的銀行都是非法的，另外全儲備銀行業務可以減少[[擠兌|擠兌]]的風險<ref>{{Citation|last=Rothbard|first=Murray N.|title=The Mystery of Banking|url=https://www.mises.org/Books/mysteryofbanking.pdf|publisher=Ludwig von Mises Institute|isbn=978-1-933550-28-2|accessdate=September 14, 2010|archive-date=2014-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141111211933/http://mises.org/Books/mysteryofbanking.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="The Case for a 100% Gold Dollar">[https://mises.org/story/1829 The Case for a 100% Gold Dollar] {{Wayback|url=https://mises.org/story/1829 |date=20090504112228 }}, Murray Rothbard</ref>。

一些經濟學家指出，由於銀行不能使用活期存款來供人[[貸款|貸款]]，因此難以從活期存款賺取的收益，認為儲戶必須支付與活期存款賬戶相關聯服務的費用。雖然多數人都瞭解到這方面的狀況，不過大眾可能會拒絕這項政策<ref name="White2003">{{Cite journal|title=Accounting for Fractional-Reserve Banknotes and Deposits—or, What’s Twenty Quid to the Bloody Midland Bank?|url=http://sensiblemoney.ie/data/documents/tir_07_3_white.pdf|last=White|first=Lawrence H.|date=Winter 2003|journal=The Independent Review|issue=3|volume=7|pages=423–41|issn=1086-1653|author=|access-date=2016-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150429081711/http://sensiblemoney.ie/data/documents/tir_07_3_white.pdf|archive-date=2015-04-29|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="Allen 1993 703–717">{{Cite journal|title=Irving Fisher and the 100 Percent Reserve Proposal|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-law-and-economics_1993-10_36_2/page/703|last=Allen|first=William|date=October 1993|journal=Journal of Law and Economics|issue=2|doi=10.1086/467295|volume=36|pages=703–17|jstor=725805}}</ref>。隨著央行零利率和[[負利率政策|負利率政策]]，一些儲戶已經開始把把自己的積蓄存入需要支付存款費用的地方甚至存入部分儲備銀行業務<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://mises.org/blog/texan-plans-build-gold-depository |title=Texan Gold Depository |accessdate=2016-07-02 |archive-date=2017-10-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171026172606/https://mises.org/blog/texan-plans-build-gold-depository |dead-url=no }}</ref>。經濟學家[[道格拉斯·戴蒙德|道格拉斯·戴蒙德]]與菲利浦H. 迪维格也警告在全儲備銀行業務下，銀行不能使用這部分的資金作借貸，會造成活期存款功能被不受監管的機構諸如[[垃圾債券|垃圾債券]]所取代，進而造成垃圾債券成為[[金融中介|金融中介]]與期限轉換，使金融體系的不穩定並造成金融危機的風險增加<ref name="Diamond-Dybvig">{{Citation|last=Diamond|first=Douglas W|title=Banking Theory, Deposit Insurance, and Bank Regulation|date=Jan 1986|quote=In conclusion, 100% reserve banking is a dangerous proposal that would do substantial damage to the economy by reducing the overall amount of liquidity. Furthermore, the proposal is likely to be ineffective in increasing stability since it will be impossible to control the institutions that will enter in the vacuum left when banks can no longer create liquidity. Fortunately, the political realities make it unlikely that this radical and imprudent proposal will be adopted.|postscript=.|coauthors=Philip H. Dybvig|series=|journal=The Journal of Business|volume=59|issue=1|pages=55–68|doi=10.1086/296314|jstor=2352687}}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal|title=Bank Runs, Deposit Insurance, and Liquidity|url=http://minneapolisfed.org/research/qr/qr2412.pdf|last=Diamond|first=Douglas|date=Winter 2000|journal=Federal Reserve Bank of Minneapolis Quarterly Review|accessdate=29 August 2012|issue=1|volume=24|pages=14–23|author2=Philip Dybvig|archive-date=2012-08-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120829034454/http://minneapolisfed.org/research/QR/QR2412.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

對於[[2007年–2008年環球金融危機|2007年–2008年環球金融危機]]的反思，[[金融時報|金融時報]]首席經濟學家[[馬丁·沃爾夫|馬丁·沃爾夫]]贊同全儲備銀行業務，並說到"這將帶來巨大的好處"<ref name="Weisenthal">{{Cite web|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/banning-banks-2014-4|title=BAN ALL THE BANKS: Here's The Wild Idea That People Are Starting To Take Seriously|publisher=Business Insider|last1=Weisenthal|first1=Joe}}</ref>，{{tsl|en|John_H._Cochrane|約翰·H·科克倫}}也認同全儲備銀行業務的優勢<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://faculty.chicagobooth.edu/john.cochrane/research/papers/run_free.pdf|title=Toward a run - free financial system|last=Cochrane|first=John|accessdate=2016-07-02|archive-date=2014-04-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140429125753/http://faculty.chicagobooth.edu/john.cochrane/research/papers/run_free.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而[[保羅·克魯格曼|保羅·克魯格曼]]在[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]的回應則是認為"全儲備銀行業務當然值得談論"，但擔心它會推動銀行體系之外的金融活動，強化了[[影子银行|影子银行]]這類較少受到規範的金融體系所<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://krugman.blogs.nytimes.com/2014/04/26/is-a-banking-ban-the-answer/?_php=true&_type=blogs&_r=0|title=Is A Banking Ban The Answer?|last=Krugman|first=Paul|date=April 26, 2014|newspaper=[[New_York_Times|New York Times]]|accessdate=September 18, 2015|archive-date=2019-12-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191208132844/https://krugman.blogs.nytimes.com/2014/04/26/is-a-banking-ban-the-answer/?_php=true&_type=blogs&_r=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

